'''2016年麦尔兹堡夜店枪击案'''是發生於2016年7月25日，[[美国|美国]][[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[麦尔兹堡|麦尔兹堡]]一家名为「Club Blu」的夜店发生的一起大规模枪击案，共造成2人死亡、至少17人受傷<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.rt.com/usa/353079-nightclub-florida-shooting-clubblu/ |title = Florida shooting: 2 confirmed killed, 14-17 injured at Club Blu nightclub in Ft. Myers |author = RT |date = 2016-07-25 |publisher = RT |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-25}}</ref>。事件发生时，夜店正在舉辦青少年派對，死伤者大多是13岁左右的青少年<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jul/25/shooting-nightclub-fort-myers-florida |title = Florida shooting: two dead outside Fort Myers nightclub |author = The Guardian |date = 2016-07-25 |publisher = The Guardian |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-25 |archive-date = 2016-07-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160726141859/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jul/25/shooting-nightclub-fort-myers-florida |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2016/07/160725_us_shooting |title = 美国佛罗里达夜店发生枪击案2死13伤 |author = BBC中文網 |date = 2016-07-25 |publisher = BBC中文網 |language = zh |accessdate = 2016-07-25 |archive-date = 2016-07-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160728130626/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2016/07/160725_us_shooting |dead-url = no }}</ref>。當地警方表示，目前在另一个地点有一人被拘留。警方在设法确枪击案的背后动机。

